<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مِن بَعْدِ ضَعْفٍ قُوَّةً}</span> ... بَعْدَ ضَعْفِ الطُّفُولَةِ قُوَّةَ الرُّجُولَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٥٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَيْبَةً}</span> ... شَيْخُوخَةً، وَهَرَمًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{غَيْرَ سَاعَةٍ}</span> ... غَيْرَ فَتْرَةٍ قَصِيرَةٍ مِنَ الزَّمَنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُؤْفَكُونَ}</span> ... يُصْرَفُونَ عَنِ الحَقِّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَعْذِرَتُهُمْ}</span> ... مَا يُقَدِّمُونَهُ مِنْ أَعْذَارٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا هُمْ يُسْتَعْتَبُونَ}</span> ... لَا يُطْلَبُ مِنْهُمْ إِرْضَاءُ اللهِ بِالطَّاعَةِ وَالتَّوْبَةِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَطْبَعُ}</span> ... يَخْتِمُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلَا يَسْتَخِفَّنَّكَ}</span> ... لَا يَسْتَفِزَّنَّكَ، وَلَا يَحْمِلَنَّكَ عَلَى الخِفَّةِ، وَالطَّيْشِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>